author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
We're back with The Indie Hour Episode Twenty-Six! This series focuses on games you may have never even heard of and gives us an inside look at the wider world of independantly published Tabletop Wargames of all genres.

This is Not a Test was one of the FIRST Indie Games ever played on GMG! Longtime friend of the channel Joey McGuire has collaborated with Ben and Connor at Black Site Studios to bring a new, ultimate 2nd Edition of the game into being with new models, beautiful art anda ton of charm. Looking for the Post-Apocalyptic ruleset that will cover any model collection? This is it. Let's dive in!

Check out the TNT Rulebook and new Accessories HERE:https://blacksitestudio.com/en-ca/collections/this-is-not-a-test-core-products
title: The GMG Indie Hour Ep 026 - This is Not a Test (2nd Edition) by Joey McGuire and Black Site Studios
